<subSubSection id="C3079AC0FFE85F58E3EEDB09FEA6FE17" pageId="14" pageNumber="15" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8BA2C94BFFE85F58E3EEDB09FEA6FE17" blockId="14.[136,1452,158,509]" pageId="14" pageNumber="15">
Notes:— 
<taxonomicName id="4C1DB2C8FFE85F58E271DB08FC8CFECF" authority="Manim., Leelav. &amp; Noordel." authorityName="Manimohan, Leelavathy &amp; Noordeloos" authorityYear="2002" box="[290,828,266,292]" class="Agaricomycetes" family="Entolomataceae" genus="Entoloma" kingdom="Fungi" order="Agaricales" pageId="14" pageNumber="15" phylum="Basidiomycota" rank="species" species="nubilum">
<emphasis id="B9691559FFE85F58E271DB08FE43FECF" box="[290,499,266,292]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="15">Entoloma nubilum</emphasis>
Manim., Leelav. &amp; Noordel.
</taxonomicName>
described from 
<collectingCountry id="F30A89DBFFE85F58E0A7DB08FB9EFECF" box="[1012,1070,266,292]" name="India" pageId="14" pageNumber="15">India</collectingCountry>
differs by the non hygrophanous, non translucent-striate pileus, smaller spores and absence of cheilocystidia (
<bibRefCitation id="EF8CB4BAFFE85F58E759DB2CFA97FEA3" author="Manimohan, P. &amp; Leelavathy, K. M. &amp; Noordeloos, M. E." box="[1034,1319,302,328]" pageId="14" pageNumber="15" pagination="625 - 630" refId="ref14580" refString="Manimohan, P., Leelavathy, K. M. &amp; Noordeloos, M. E. (2002) Three new species of Entoloma from Kerala State, India. Persoonia 17: 625 - 630." type="journal article" year="2002">
