<bibRefCitation id="EF8CB4BAFFE85F58E7F4DB98FA2CFE5E" author="Saccardo, P. A." box="[1191,1436,410,437]" pageId="14" pageNumber="15" refId="ref15692" refString="Saccardo, P. A. (1887) Sylloge fungorum omnium hucusque cognitorum vol 5. Sumptibus auctoris, Patavii. 1146 pp. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 5371" type="book" year="1887">Saccardo (1887: 688)</bibRefCitation>
